item.title: I have no Idea how to run stuff
item.dc:creator: @Rune_Hacker1 Rune Hacker
item.description:
@Rune_Hacker1 wrote:

When you open up Scar, click on File at the top left, click in Download SRL, wait until that is done, then click the option below that which is called Download Includes. Then wait for that to finish and Scar should work. If it doesnt, please post here.
